title: Earned an S with Quinn just now and didn't get my chest.
body:
https://gyazo.com/883aaa3bc6ace2940017d15f2a5f9029

You can view my match history.

replies.body: You account is showing that you've [**already earned a chest for Quinn this season**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/207884233). Keep in mind that you can only get one chest for each champion per season. You do still have 4 open chests, but you'll have to earn them on champions you've haven't gotten a chest with.
